headline: Kristy Carstensen takes over as leader of U.S. Bank Global Treasury Management
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 25, 2024--U.S. Bank announced Kristy Carstensen as the new leader of its Global Treasury Management business. In this position, Carstensen heads the unit that provides comprehensive treasury management and payment solutions to the bank’s business, government and institutional clients. In addition to Global Treasury Management, Carstensen will also oversee the bank’s prepaid card organization.
